narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Interesting materials on language and translation.
I would summarize it as a class for those who want to get real experience doing translation in a small classroom. It was a class that I always was excited to go to. I would highly recommend it.

the course was a lot of fun, especially if you have other engaged students in the class, so it's definitely one to shop to see who else wants to take it. otherwise, the course is pretty free-form so you get what you put into it.
Take it if you're interested in translation. Or in different languages.
